{"type": "article", "id": 22425, "title": "这本“最可爱的怀孕日记”，还能表现身形的变化", "description": "随着书页的翻动，你能感觉人体奇妙的改变。", "date": "2016-02-18T07:56:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6035, "name": "手帐"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 23552, "name": "书籍装帧"}, {"id": 23553, "name": "Mother Booking"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 243, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021541245Ufgn946ioepLSxJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>最近，日本出现了一种<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/02/16/40-week-mother-book-pregnancy-diary-grows-with-the-mothers-belly/\">“妈妈手帐”</a>，手帐共有 40 页，妈妈们可以在上面写 40 周的妊娠日记，每周一页。手帐的精妙之处在于，它是全手工打造的，且每一页镂空的大小不同，随着书页的翻动，书页会呈现出女性身体的变化，颇为可爱。除此之外，它还会普及一些关于胚胎发育的知识，算得上是科学、平面装帧和剪纸艺术的融合了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154119zhOcwTVnkrFAbvqZ.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">每一页镂空的大小不同，翻动书页时，自然就形成了人身的形态</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215411998axfQ3Yw6XyzGNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">手帐第一页</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154120TejhUmcpRwGANLvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">手帐第二十八页，也是第二十八周</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154121weMIZabphYSzs53D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62529002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计细节</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">其实早在 2014 年日本就出现过这款手帐了。它是广告公司电通和医疗公司 Kishokai 共同设计的。那时候，它就凭借着“最可爱的怀孕日记”的名声赢得了无数奖项。鉴于巨大的反响，设计师们又制作了许多副本，现在任何人都可在网站上购买了，精装本售价 30000 日元，简装本售价为 3980 日元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154121GfX2nJKowpxqeCsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154122yf2In9UYDCE3e5tV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021541228Sf3rDguKnEBAhRx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">以上是日本孕妈妈写的手帐，空白处可供妈妈们写下心情感触</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>如果你对这款手帐感兴趣，可以访问它的<a href=\"http://modelight.shop-pro.jp\">官方网站</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021541237DWt3ALyShzUpMdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2014/11/07/mother-book-a-pregnancy-diary-that-grows-with-the-mothers-belly/\">spoon-tamago</a></p>\n\n\n"}